Clipboard - Copy and paste with any OS

Who doesn't remember the first time they learned to copy and paste, and generated
an exponentially growing text document? Yes, that's right, clipboards are magical.

With Clipboard.pm, this magic is now trivial to access, cross-platformly, from your Perl code.
